Poverty levels have increased, societal bonds strained and the overall trend of development reversed.Yet we have witnessed stories of hope, courage, triumph and kindness: The spirit of oneness — Ubuntu. For most of 2020, our lives were disrupted by Covid-19. Lives have been lost, livelihoods disrupted and education adversely impacted.
Poverty levels have increased, societal bonds strained and the overall trend of development reversed.
Yet we have witnessed stories of hope, courage, triumph and kindness: The spirit of oneness — Ubuntu, Obuntubulamu or Utu — as is commonly known in East and Southern Africa regions.



